íŸ@69eb4e172037cb5d206c5be8e79b1ee7b6144dcf798ae0dc7a266462aa731822⁄;Title: title: save
Path: Flags
Content:
``--stderr, -e {path}``
: The filename used to save stderr, only works with 
``-r``
 flag.
``--raw, -r``
: Save file as raw binary.
``--append, -a``
: Append input to the end of the file.
``--force, -f``
: Overwrite the destination.
``--progress, -p``
: Enable progress bar.
